 “Islands Of Insight”是一款受神经科学和美感启发的开放世界益智游戏https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/islands-of-insight-puzzles-adventure-open-world-3564541?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=islands-of-insight-puzzles-adventure-open-世界Andy BrownTue, 02 Jan 2024 15:08:54 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3564541 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="洞察力岛屿。图片来源：Lunarch Studios。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>期待一个“远离传统”的故事和大量的“尤里卡时刻”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/islands-of-insight-puzzles-adventure-open-world-3564541">《Islands Of Insight》是一款受神经科学和美感启发的开放世界益智游戏，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="洞察力岛屿。图片来源：Lunarch Studios。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在奇幻益智游戏<em>《Islands Of Insight》</em>下个月推出之前， <em>NME</em>采访了游戏总监 Elyot Grant，了解该游戏对其类型的不同寻常的处理方式。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/best-games-2023-switch-xbox-playstation-pc-3551161">2023 年 20 款最佳游戏</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>《Islands Of Insight》</em>将要求玩家完成基于谜题的任务，并了解游戏宇宙中发生了什么——这看起来更像是角色扮演冒险的背景，而不是传统的益智游戏。</p><p> “对我们来说，谜题可以很美丽，甚至令人惊叹，我们觉得超凡脱俗的奇幻主题比卡通图形或更简单的环境更符合这一点，”开发商 Lunarch Studios 的游戏总监兼首席执行官埃利奥特·格兰特 (Elyot Grant) 解释道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="洞察岛|揭晓预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PN47pZrXH0A?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我们渴望创造出更具影响力的东西，美丽的环境将为游戏增添丰富感和惊奇感，”他们补充道。 “我们还看到了大量以奇幻为主题的游戏——动作冒险、角色扮演游戏——以谜题为特色，但通常作为配菜而不是主菜。我们认为，通过首先关注这种风格中的谜题，我们可以创造出一些受人喜爱且有些熟悉的东西，同时也能提高艺术水平。”</p><p>同样， <em>《洞察之岛》</em>的故事“远非传统”，将涉及收集已知王国居民的记忆碎片。为了弄清楚世界上发生了什么，玩家需要将这些记忆拼凑起来——这意味着即使是情节本身也是一个谜题。</p><p>格兰特认为，世界的传说受到“数学、神经科学、美与崇高的哲学、世界各地的诗歌和谚语、经典文学[和]宇宙学”以及“许多其他事物”的启发。 </p><figure id="attachment_3564585" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3564585" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3564585" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-2.jpg" alt="洞察力岛屿。图片来源：Lunarch Studios。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Islands-Of-Insight-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3564585" class="wp-caption-text">洞察力岛屿。图片来源：Lunarch Studios。</figcaption></figure><p>至于谜题本身，Lunarch Studios 围绕“顿悟时刻”设计了每个挑战，供玩家探索。</p><p>格兰特分享道：“我们选择的谜题机制能够支持一系列深刻而广泛的顿悟时刻，同时也尝试最大限度地增加多样性并平衡节奏和难度，以防止你大脑的某一部分过于疲劳。” “我们的谜题设计师将谜题本身作为表达创造力的画布，因为您会发现许多秘密主题、模式或聪明点，您可以在解决问题的过程中解开它们。”</p><p> <em>《Islands Of Insight》</em>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/behaviour-interactive">Behavior Interactive</a>发行，该公司以其多人恐怖游戏<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dead-by-daylight">《Dead By Daylight》</a></em>而闻名。</p><p> 2024 年对于该工作室来说将是忙碌的一年，因为它还将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/supermassive-games">Supermassive Games</a>合作发布“沉浸式噩梦” <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2223840/The_Casting_of_Frank_Stone/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《弗兰克·斯通选角》</em></a> 。</p><p>至于<em>《黎明杀机》</em> ，这款恐怖游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/alien-crossover-in-dead-by-daylight-adds-ripley-jonesy-and-the-nostromo-3480377">终于在 2023 年迎来了期待已久的<em>异形</em>联动</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/islands-of-insight-puzzles-adventure-open-world-3564541">《Islands Of Insight》是一款受神经科学和美感启发的开放世界益智游戏，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
